  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t學班藍絲同共匪話齋，好人好姐冇做犯法嘢/壞事點解咁驚人知道事實，唔見得光一定身有屎<br/>\n<br/>\r\n中共八九六四行得正企得正，怕咩畀人講<br/>\n<br/>\r\n港共政權高調拉人，擺明係抹黑共產黨#:)#b<br/>\n<br/>\r\n每年北京處理手法不嬲都係低調處理，中國香港忠誠廢物高調拉人不斷宣傳8964又幫中國添煩添亂，香港政府果然係最大叛亂勢力<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTZiNDkyOTgwMDU3MzQ3Mzk5ZDk2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/96b492980057347399d96.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/96b492980057347399d96.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/96b492980057347399d96.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGJjMzRlODY3ZmYwZGRhZDJhNjRkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dbc34e867ff0ddad2a64d.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dbc34e867ff0ddad2a64d.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dbc34e867ff0ddad2a64d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDEzMGU2M2JkZjQwZjI1MTkwNTQ2LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d130e63bdf40f25190546.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d130e63bdf40f25190546.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d130e63bdf40f25190546.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2JiMTQxMjU4MTcwMjVkMDgwMWU1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cbb14125817025d0801e5.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cbb14125817025d0801e5.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cbb14125817025d0801e5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjdhYTMwYzA3NGYzYzhlMzFiYjMzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow 